Package: haldane
Title: haldane: Tools for malaria genomics
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: "Stuart Lee <lee.s@wehi.edu.au> [aut, cre]"
Description: R package to manipulate and analyse next generation sequencing data from malaria
    parasites. haldane can be used to simulate data under multipcicity of
    infection, population genetics analysis of isolate populations, and
    simulation of data produced by Fluidigm dynamic array technology.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.1.1)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
Imports: SeqArray, ggbio, ggplot2, GenomicRanges, S4Vectors
Suggests: testthat,
    knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
